Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.85,0:00:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.68,0:00:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.39,0:00:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.36,0:00:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.14,0:00:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.95,0:00:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.62,0:00:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.99,0:00:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.09,0:01:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.70,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.14,0:01:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.81,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.18,0:01:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.72,0:01:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.30,0:01:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新年才剛過完沒多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.07,0:01:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,青少年們就開始失控浮躁起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,客人,客人\N你是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.19,0:02:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.76,0:02:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔,明天就是第一次共通考試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.87,0:02:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.21,0:02:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.86,0:02:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#03 暗夜中心跳不已\N和響子單獨相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,考生真是辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要對五代多關心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.67,0:02:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正是最後的緊要關頭\N他一定緊張得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遜斃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好醜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.49,0:03:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次共通考試\N明天終於要登場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.16,0:03:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有自信嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白痴,有自信我就不會煩惱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.33,0:03:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.54,0:03:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知道這一年\N就應該更努力用功一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.74,0:03:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼都還沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.65,0:03:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什麼都沒做嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,連手都還沒牽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.79,0:03:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有什麼\N當然是管理員的事囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.86,0:03:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在什麼都還沒做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.46,0:03:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,競爭對手又少了一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得去跟四谷和朱美他們說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請他們不要吵五代唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.56,0:04:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好冷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先從朱美開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.32,0:04:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳幹嘛啊?有什麼事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒…沒事,請快點過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.71,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,快點過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.15,0:05:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,妳是怎麼了啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好冷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿這麼少當然會冷囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在看什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣的話\N你鐵定會重考第二次喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶,重考第二次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,妳找我有什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.72,0:05:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天五代要參加第一次共通考試\N我想告訴妳不要刺激他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.56,0:05:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要穿得這麼清涼\N在公寓裡走來走去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.93,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我剛才想對妳說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!不准看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會是不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.78,0:06:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,你不在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.59,0:06:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,四谷不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.09,0:06:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不幸中的大幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕快趁現在來個總複習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜猜我是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷出現了,四谷出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.81,0:06:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜對了,你怎麼會知道呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.09,0:07:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,原來你在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼時候來的?\N從哪裡進來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從剛剛一直就在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.43,0:07:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於我是怎麼進來的嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(秘密)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又挖了一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.97,0:07:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我的祕密通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這算哪門子的祕密通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,你立刻離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你好冷漠喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.62,0:07:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.62,0:07:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,今天對五代而言\N是非常重要的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以再對他惡作劇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員為了我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶好耶,終於進入狀況了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.66,0:08:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼聲音啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.46,0:08:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快趴下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.96,0:08:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹嘛打我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼去外面玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,這個走廊最好滑了\N(“滑”音同“落榜”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你居然說了我最忌諱的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被重考生打了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.64,0:09:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這麼一句話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳就沒有別的話說了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍耐吧,汁夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麵子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人明天要考試\N脾氣難免大了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.13,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重考生就可以為所欲為嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.77,0:09:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以打弱小的小孩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等考完試再加倍奉還就行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麵子,妳一定要等我到考試通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汁夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等不了那麼久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼這個社會\N都對重考生那麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在走廊溜滑板有什麼不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滑板不能滑的話\N還有什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.17,0:10:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也說說話啊,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不能說“滑”這個字!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.11,0:10:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滑!滑!我想要溜滑板!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要溜滑板,我想要溜滑板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賢太郎,不要再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.62,0:10:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之進屋裡去就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,我不要進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冬天的…雨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.35,0:10:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不會變成淚雨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白天沒有唸到的部分\N要一口氣追回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.13,0:11:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.06,0:11:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要把我的房間當作宴會廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡早就變成宴會廳了\N有什麼辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳來幹嘛?妳來幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.38,0:11:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,妳不是說考試要到了\N不可以吵重考生嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.39,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係啦,他已經變成\N沒聽到宴會吵鬧聲就無法唸書了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.66,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒有呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.80,0:12:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正明天他一定會很沮喪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.47,0:12:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要好好地瘋一瘋\N讓他壯烈地成仁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.77,0:12:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說你們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,你們又…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我鄭重地再說一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,考試的季節就要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.39,0:12:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請暫時不要去吵五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在五代面前絕對不能說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.13,0:12:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考\N之類的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連開玩笑都不能喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.11,0:12:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說不能說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.71,0:12:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還用問嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳大聲一點再說一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.35,0:13:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.62,0:13:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.95,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要出去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.87,0:13:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚我要去朋友家唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滑倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這實在太有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,你真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛起來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼可能辦得到!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.15,0:14:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為你一定辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.32,0:14:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,這是什麼爛環境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.39,0:14:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鞋…鞋帶斷掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這代表…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不吉祥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.04,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這已經超越了\N“不吉祥”這個字能形容的範圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要氣餒,明年還有機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.98,0:14:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別用這種奇怪的話安慰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.38,0:14:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼這麼說\N四谷說得沒錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,對啊\N明年考不上的話,還有後年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,你們不要太過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.92,0:14:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然我真的要生氣囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳幹嘛氣成這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她從白天就一直怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.07,0:15:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了\N管理員對重考生有意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不要胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.04,0:15:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不出面的話\N你們一定會沒完沒了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敷衍、欺騙、前後不一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員的臉變紅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是為五代著想而已…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是…我只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你改變主意不出門了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.99,0:15:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.03,0:15:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了回報妳的一片真心\N我會加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全認真起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還真樂觀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.81,0:15:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好累…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員對我有所期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我們這一棟停電耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.52,0:16:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是保險絲燒斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你要唸書…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.06,0:16:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停電怎麼唸書呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.66,0:16:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪,保險絲沒有異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會是配線出了問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.47,0:16:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話,先看看配線圖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳會修嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會,且工具都很齊全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.68,0:16:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對維修也略懂一二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該在這裡面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.75,0:16:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.92,0:17:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是第一次來這個閣樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人獨處在暗室裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.31,0:17:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來這裡是個鐘塔小屋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.04,0:17:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,那個壞掉的時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.29,0:17:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有種古老圖書館的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像古董店的店頭擺飾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.07,0:17:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一刻館的歷史真的很悠久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.25,0:18:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼時候建的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再會了,青春的一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昭和15年(1940年)3月13日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.60,0:18:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,期待再相逢\N昭和19年(1944年)10月17日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是在戰爭期間寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.48,0:19:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那個時代\N愛上一個人一定很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.42,0:19:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.72,0:19:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭不曉得拆散了多少對情侶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.36,0:19:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們活著的這個時代\N真是和平啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.03,0:19:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.73,0:19:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.54,0:19:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是以前住在這裡的人\N已經變成回憶的青春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.98,0:19:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是一刻館的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.91,0:19:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我會喜歡上一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.87,0:20:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給小櫻\N昭和19年(1944年),一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是一段沒有結局的愛情嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.55,0:20:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心看出神了,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.22,0:20:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.79,0:20:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得快點把停電修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.59,0:20:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我得努力把它修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為明天是你的重要日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.74,0:20:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員\N什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.17,0:20:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳為了我這麼認真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.71,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,你誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.74,0:20:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是為了你著想,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…等等,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.72,0:20:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.49,0:20:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒醒啊,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.46,0:21:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想說你們一直沒回來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.36,0:21:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧,來吧\N不用在意我們,請繼續下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在胡說些什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.81,0:21:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.28,0:21:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在對她養的狗道歉耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.72,0:21:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她剛才摔倒的時候\N好像有撞到頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一隻老鼠燒焦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是牠咬斷了電線啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.76,0:22:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.94,0:22:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.15,0:22:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼聲音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.52,0:22:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是時鐘的聲音吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.12,0:22:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這個時鐘早就壞掉了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理應壞了的鐘塔時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.77,0:22:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不曉得為什麼突然響了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.30,0:22:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怖的鐘聲,在下著雨的城鎮中\N整夜響個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.25,0:23:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正整晚都沒睡\N順便出來送你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.19,0:23:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會再開宴會安慰你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.96,0:23:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡力而為吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.69,0:23:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請好好加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,那我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.37,0:23:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他滑得還真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.64,0:23:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下沒救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.76,0:23:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.63,0:23:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這句話已經持續說了一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.87,0:23:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.70,0:23:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還是遲遲沒有上榜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.27,0:24:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回\N『響子緊張萬分?五代考試中』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.94,0:24:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事?\N他居然從考場逃了出來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.78,0:24:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天我要陪他去應考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.50,0:24:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.81,0:24:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.95,0:24:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能讓我悸動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.85,0:24:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我身陷險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.09,0:24:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已經可以相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.63,0:25:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏偏時機還不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.07,0:25:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快要忍受不了\N快要變成了愚蠢的男人
